{"tid":1340918,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"除了武鬥，文鬥同樣重要：交稅不合作運動","createTime":"2019-07-21T16:19:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T16:24:36.000Z","uid":273188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"37c8a00c5011d6de780f28e21b0b43f6ad05de0a","tid":1340918,"uid":273188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:19:38.000Z","msg":"大家記得申請定多本支票簿。<br />\n今年，大家一定要試下。<br />\nref: <a href=\"http://www.inmediahk.net/node/1029260\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1029260&d=PG0fnU9ECAVDedUX85NM%2FNUqyFx8t7fe88%2BQEXu6%2F%2FM%3D&h=54af5c2f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1029260&h=468de21b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.inmediahk.net/node/1029260</a><br />\n例如分開多張支票交稅，如一萬元的稅款分開十五次繳交（頭十四次每次689元，以諷刺梁振英由689位選委選出）。只要在期限前交稅，這個方法是完全合法的。另一個做法，是透過電子銀行以信用卡分開多次交稅，對政府的行政影響較少，而銀行會向政府收取手續費用。"},{"pid":"f1b2183bb8bb96c178dc3da3534ee7b4b7d3881d","tid":1340918,"uid":273188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:24:36.000Z","msg":"推"}]}